&lt;p&gt;The Brattle Group answers complex economic, finance, and regulatory questions for corporations, law firms, and governments around the world. We are distinguished by the clarity of our insights and the credibility of our experts, which include leading international academics and industry specialists. Brattle has over 450 talented professionals across four continents. For more information, please visit &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.brattle.com/&quot;&gt;our website.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
