&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The ideal candidate will possess:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A PhD in Finance, Financial Economics, or Accounting or an MBA with an academic or professional background in Finance or Accounting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent foundation in quantitative analysis, and/or several years of relevant work experience (preferably in economic consulting, public accounting, investment banking, or similar environment)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven project management skills, with the ability to effectively collaborate with multiple stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated record of outstanding academic and/or professional accomplishment&lt;/li&gt;
