&lt;li&gt;Coordinate extensive domestic and international travel for Principals (and occasionally other team members) to client meetings and/or marketing opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In conjunction with Marketing, research and identify external targets for monthly business development purposes including outreach and meeting scheduling; coordinate external speaking opportunities including tracking dates, providing materials to organizers, assisting with presentations, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure Principals’ resumes and bios are regularly updated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and submit expense reports and assist Principals with expense approvals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist Principals with their calendars including day-to-day schedules/tasks and suggest ways to maximize Principals’ time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate, prepare agendas, create PowerPoint slides, and attend all practice area meetings; provide catering and meeting set-up as needed; document and distribute action items from practice area meetings to attendees and any necessary follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initiate and/or coordinate Project Start Forms, conflict checks, engagement letters and proposals with Principals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with monthly invoicing and project budgets with Project Managers and/or Associates assigned to cases as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand client contracts to determine monthly billing requirements, including write-offs and holds with minimal Principal oversight in some cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide monthly and/or weekly budget updates as needed/directed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross functionally with other offices and departments such as Accounting, Legal, and Marketing to ensure all project or corporate obligations are met both individually and for principals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with event planning as directed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide Reception coverage and back-up support to other BSS team members in their absence and/or when their workload necessitates support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide back-up support and assistance to Facilities Services Assistants as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;THE CANDIDATE&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree preferred; will consider experience in lieu of degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Requires a minimum of three (3) years executive/senior-level administrative experience, preferably in a professional services field and team environments&lt;/l

