&lt;p&gt;Please submit the following materials through the link below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cover letter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resume&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transcript(s) (unofficial copies accepted)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brattle offers a competitive benefits package, base salary, and bonus program for eligible roles based on individual and firm performance.&lt;/p&gt;
